[OverTheWire](https://overthewire.org/wargames/) is a free platform to learn and practice security concepts through hands-on wargames. [Bandit](https://overthewire.org/wargames/bandit/) is the recommended starting point — it covers the Linux and Git fundamentals you'll need for every other game on the platform.

