##  Common Mistakes

| Mistake | What Happens | Fix |
|--------|--------------|-----|
| Forgetting `-p 2220` | `Connection refused` error | Always include `-p 2220` for OTW |
| Typing password wrong | `Permission denied` | Re-run the command and retype carefully |
| Expecting password echo | Looks like nothing is being typed | Normal — just type and press Enter |
